I use [this build script](https://gist.github.com/Calinou/44edbd5d9c4a2ac0dbc8f165b8b7f0ce) to compile for Android from Windows. [MinGW-w64](http://mingw-w64.org) 5.4.0 (also tried with 6.2.0), Android SDK (with all required tools) and NDK are installed.

